views.markdown: If you need help with "Jailbreak Status Bar Icons", you can contact Randomblock1, the developer, via e-mail.
Randomblock1 is the maintainer of the package "Jailbreak Status Bar Icons". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "Randomblock1's Repo" repo, Randomblock1.
